<h id='fromTheitJustWorksDepartment'><a href="https://w3future.com/weblog/2005/03/07.xml#a285" class="weblogItemTitle">From the &#8220;It just works&#8221; department</a></h>
<p>Why isn't everybody talking about <a href="http://www.hamachi.cc/">Hamachi</a> yet? I can't think of an easier way to create VPNs. It looks great and it has a very nice start-up quick tutorial. It's great for playing games with friends over the internet. No more wrestling with configuring routers and firewalls, it just works!</p><p>Why doesn't Microsoft release a p2p network driver? They have <a href="http://www.threedegrees.com/">the technology</a>.</p>
